OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'Grammer' School:          
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FLancashire council's sign  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ferror amuses pupils        
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A council has promised it "must try    
OL,6, harder" after misspelling a leading    
OL,7, school as a "grammer".                 
OL,9,FHeadmaster Chris Pyle spotted the error
OL,10,Fon a new bus stop sign outside         
OL,11,FLancaster Royal Grammar School (LRGS). 
OL,13,F"We are enjoying the irony," said Dr   
OL,14,FPyle, "but will keep on trying to teach
OL,15,Fthe world how to spell 'grammar'       
OL,16,Fcorrectly."                            
OL,18,FLancashire County Council said the     
OL,19,F"schoolboy error" would be corrected   
OL,20,Fover the coming days.                  
